  "subject": "Add Jetty deobfuscation of topic password",
  "commit_message": "Add Jetty deobfuscation of topic password\n\nThe event topic password configured in the event configuration\nproperty files (event-consumer.properties, event-publisher.properties)\nis obfuscated using the Jetty password obfuscation tool.\nBefore both the consumer and publisher event beans are instantiated\nthe topic password needs to be deobfuscated.\n\nChange-Id: I54428a97eb91dcc7360699d06693f6aa85a25319\nIssue-ID: AAI-1384\nSigned-off-by: Michael Arrastia <MArrasti@amdocs.com>\n",
